# Run strict typecheck before every git push.
# This catches the "undeclared variable / stringly-typed IPC" class of bug
# that electron-vite build silently lets through.
#
# To bypass in a genuine emergency (hotfix, CI outage), use:
#   git push --no-verify
# Only use --no-verify when you have already run `pnpm typecheck` locally and
# know the code is clean; the CI typecheck in release.yml will block the
# daily build if types are broken.

pnpm typecheck
